I noticed you were looking for access to the PDFs. Great news - you have several options to get them!

You can access all the PDFs through any of these POWLAX products:

1. Printable Playbooks ($99) - Get immediate access to all the grab-and-go visual playbooks and practice plans you can print anytime.

2. Coaching Kits( $149) - These include printable practice plans with clear instructions, drill diagrams, and coaching tips that you can keep in your pocket during practice.

3. Team HQ Platform (Starting at $349) - This gives you the complete hub with digital and printable playbooks, practice plans, and all team resources in one place.

4. Club OS (starting at $299/team) - If you're part of a club, this includes everything above plus additional coaching resources and tools for the entire organization.

All of these options give you full access to download and print the PDFs whenever you need them. The printable resources are designed to be simple, clear, and ready to use - just open, print, and go!

Which option would work best for your needs? I'm happy to help you get set up with the right solution.

Let me know if you have any questions!
